224
00:17:05,420 --> 00:17:07,890
I showed my heart.

225
00:17:07,890 --> 00:17:10,250
(I showed it to you instead of using words.)

226
00:17:12,660 --> 00:17:15,819
(Bi-so is tired of hiding it any longer.)

227
00:17:15,819 --> 00:17:17,140
But...

228
